# Design System

Monochrome palette: **black · white · greys**. No color accents. Surfaces are solid fills or Liquid Glass.

## Colors — use `GGColor` only

```swift
// ✅
.background(GGColor.bg)
.foregroundStyle(GGColor.textPrimary)
.background(Capsule().fill(GGColor.white)) // CTAs; text uses GGColor.onAccent (black)

// ❌ Colored accents (blue / red / green themes)
```

- Surfaces: `bg`, `surface`, `surface2`, `darkGrey`, `hairline`
- Text: `textPrimary`, `textSecondary`, `textTertiary`
- Accent tokens (`accent`, `blue`, `success`) resolve to white; `onAccent` is black

## Typography

- UI: SF Pro via `.font(.gg(size, weight))` or `.system(...)`
- Explanatory copy: New York via `.explanatory` / `.ny`
- Chips/meta: `.ggMono`

## Glass & media

- Cards/pills: `.glass(...)` / `.glassCapsule(...)` / `.liquidGlass(...)`
- Brand: `Wordmark` (`gojo` + muted trailing `go`)
- Madeleine: white disc + black sparkles
